      * Hæmta detta ena ærendet.

     C     Error         IFEQ      *blanks
N01  c                   IF        OPDN<>0
     C     FREEKEY       CHAIN     FREETXT1                           55
N01  c                   ELSE
N01  C     ZREEKEY       CHAIN     ZREETXT2                           55
N01  c                   ENDIF
     C     *IN55         IFEQ      '0'
